<li>Student progress notes</li>
<li>Schedule viewing</li>
<li>Student contact access</li>
</ul>

<h3>10. Reporting and Analytics</h3>

<p>Data-driven decision making requires accessible reporting. Essential reports include:</p>

<ul>
<li>Revenue and financial summaries</li>
<li>Membership statistics and trends</li>
<li>Attendance patterns and utilisation</li>
</ul>

<ul>
<li>Retention and churn analysis</li>
<li>Belt testing and progression metrics</li>
<li>Lead and trial conversion tracking</li>
</ul>

<ul>
